近年來發表之代表著作
SCI(期刊)論文





1.


Kuo-Tung Jiann and Peng Ho, 2014. Cadmium mixing behavior in estuaries: Redox controls on removal and mobilization. Terrestrial, Atmospheric and Oceanic Sciences, 25(5), 655-664. DOI: 10.3319/TAO.2014.04.01.01(Oc)




2.


Kuo-Tung Jiann, Liang-Saw Wen and Ching-Ling Wei, 2014. Spatial and temporal distribution of trace metals (Cd, Cu, Ni, Pb, and Zn) in near-shore waters off the west coast of Taiwan. Terrestrial, Atmospheric and Oceanic Sciences, 25(1), 121-135.DOI: 10.3319/TAO.2013.09.13.01(Oc)




3.


Kuo-Tung Jiann, Peter H. Santschi and Bobby J. Presley, 2013. Relationships between geochemical parameters (pH, DOC, SPM, EDTA concentrations) and trace metal (Cd, Co, Cu, Fe, Mn, Ni, Pb, Zn) concentrations in river waters of Texas (USA). Aquatic Geochemistry, 19(2), 173-193. DOI: 10.1007/s10498-013-9187-6




4.


Ching-Ling Wei, Kuo-Tung Jiann, Liang-Saw Wen, and David D.-D.Sheu, 2012. Distributions and removal fluxes of trace metals in the water column of the Hung-Tsai Trough off southwestern Taiwan. Marine Pollution Bulletin, 64(6), 1122-1128. doi: 10.1016/j.marpolbul.2012.03.032




5.


Kuo-Tung Jiann and Liang-Saw Wen, 2012. Distribution and lability of dissolved iron in surface waters of marginal seas in southeastern Asia. Estuarine, Coastal and Shelf Science, 100, 142-149 doi:10.1016/j.ecss.2012.01.006




6.


Liang-Saw Wen, Peter H. Santschi, Kent W. Warnken, William Davison, Hao Zhang, Hsiu-Ping Li and Kuo-Tung Jiann, 2011. Molecular weight and chemical reactivity of dissolved trace metals (Cd, Cu, Ni) in surface waters from the Mississippi River to Gulf of Mexico. Estuarine, Coastal and Shelf Science, 92, 649-658. Doi: 10.1016/j.ecss.2011.03.009




7.


Ching-Ling Wei, Kuo-Tung Jiann, Liang-Saw Wen, Jing-Ru Tsai and David D. Sheu, 2011. Removal fluxes of Mn and Fe from the nearshore waters along the west coast of Taiwan. Marine Pollution Bulletin, 62, 1081-1087. Doi: 10.1016/j.marpolbul.2011.01.039




